  <summary date="2021-10-30T16:46:11Z" status="Introduced in House">Helping Medicaid Offer Maternity Services Act of 2021 or the Helping MOMS Act of 2021

This bill permanently allows states to provide one year of postpartum coverage under Medicaid and temporarily increases the Federal Medical Assistance Percentage (i.e., federal matching rate) for pregnancy-related services in states that choose to do so.</summary>
